<item>
            <title>[FLINK-6294] BucketingSink throws NPE while cancelling job</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6294</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;configure BucketingSink and run job&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;cancel job from UI before processing any messages&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;in logs:
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;2017-04-11 10:14:54,681 INFO  org.apache.flink.core.fs.FileSystem                           - Ensuring all FileSystem streams are closed &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; Source: Custom Source (1/2) [Source: Custom Source (1/2)]
